::Battera::

She walks down the corridoor and goes to the conference room where 
Iron Raptor is.  She stands in the doorway and looks arond.  She 
looks at Iron Raptor.  "Pardon me, I was told you are the leader of 
the maximal group.  I was wondering if I might have a word with you?"
